         <abstract>
            <p>In this paper, we identify univariate prewavelets on spaces spanned by translates of multiquadric functions and other radial basis functions with nonequally spaced centers (or "knots"). Although the multiquadratic function and its relations are our prime examples, the theory is sufficiently broad to admit prewavelets from other radial basis function spaces as well.</p>
          </abstract>
